{
  "stem": "19969.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And about half of them rushed up to the gate and got it closed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "The woman got frightened in the meantime.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And she ran back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Well, before she went in there, she said to me, she said, Colonel, I, I want to interview some important prisoners.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "She said-- Cardinal Niemoller, she said.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Well, I'd never heard of Cardinal Niemoller.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And the Prince of Luxembourg-- and she gave one other name that I didn't catch.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Well, I said, I don't know anything about them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "But you can't go in there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And, while I'm talking to the general, she did anyway.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "Well, she ran back after the firing started and got in her jeep.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And then the general and I got into a pretty heated argument.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "He said, I'm relieving you of command.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And I'm taking responsibility.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "I says, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "You-- this is my area.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "You're not relieving me of command.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So finally, I said to one of the privates standing there, I said, Private, escort this general and his party out of here.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had come in the main gate to the-- to the whole-- to the whole compound-- to the whole area, which is about two blocks from this prison gate.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] well, the private stepped forward.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He didn't know what what the hell to do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this general carried a little, old stick, I don't know, a swagger stick or riding crop [POINTING] about that long with him.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was a rather short guy, a little pudgy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as the private approached the jeep, he whacked him over the helmet with his stick.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, it had already been a long, trying day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I exploded at that point.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I hauled out my .45.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
